<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Media Manager</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#f8f9fa] min-h-screen font-sans text-slate-800">
    <nav class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between h-16 items-center">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="bg-slate-900 p-2 rounded-lg">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">Media Manager</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <a href="/admin" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 text-sm font-semibold transition">Back to Dashboard</a>
                    <span class="w-px h-4 bg-gray-300"></span>
                    <a href="/main" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900 text-sm font-medium transition">Main</a>
                    <span class="w-px h-4 bg-gray-300"></span>
                    <a href="/browse" class="text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900 text-sm font-medium transition">Storefront</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10">
    <div class="mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">Manage Media Files</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Upload and organize images and assets used throughout the platform.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-[0_2px_8px_-3px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] p-6 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 tracking-tight mb-5 border-b border-gray-100 pb-4">Upload New Image</h2>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="mb-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-red-200 bg-red-50 text-red-700 font-medium text-sm shadow-sm"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>
      <% if (uploaded) { %>
        <div class="mb-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 font-medium text-sm shadow-sm flex flex-col gap-3">
            <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> Success! Uploaded to: <code class="bg-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs select-all"><%= uploaded %></code></span>
            <img src="<%= uploaded %>" alt="uploaded file" class="w-48 h-32 object-cover rounded-lg border border-emerald-200 shadow-sm mt-2">
        </div>
      <% } %>

      <form action="/admin/media/upload" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="space-y-5">
        <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= csrfToken %>">

        <div>
          <label class="block mb-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Storage Category</label>
          <select name="category" class="w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/20 focus:border-indigo-500 transition-all bg-slate-50" required>
            <% categories.forEach((category) => { %>
              <option value="<%= category %>"><%= category %></option>
            <% }) %>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label class="block mb-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Bind to Product Camera (Optional)</label>
          <select name="cameraId" class="w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/20 focus:border-indigo-500 transition-all bg-slate-50">
            <option value="">-- No binding --</option>
            <% cameras.forEach((camera) => { %>
              <option value="<%= camera.id %>"><%= camera.brand %> <%= camera.model %> (ID <%= camera.id %>)</option>
            <% }) %>
          </select>
          <p class="text-[13px] text-slate-500 mt-2 flex items-center gap-1.5"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg> If folder is <code>products</code> and camera is selected, system updates camera image path automatically.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label class="block mb-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Image File</label>
          <input type="file" name="imageFile" accept=".jpg,.jpeg,.png,.webp,.gif,.svg" class="w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/20 focus:border-indigo-500 transition-all file:mr-4 file:py-2 file:px-4 file:rounded-md file:border-0 file:text-sm file:font-semibold file:bg-indigo-50 file:text-indigo-700 hover:file:bg-indigo-100 cursor-pointer" required>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-2">
            <button type="submit" class="bg-indigo-600 text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-indigo-700 hover:shadow-md transition-all w-full md:w-auto">Upload & Process</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-[0_2px_8px_-3px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] p-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 tracking-tight mb-4 border-b border-gray-100 pb-3">Folder Structure</h2>
      <pre class="bg-slate-800 text-emerald-400 rounded-xl p-5 text-sm font-mono overflow-x-auto shadow-inner">public/
  uploads/
    ├── products/
    ├── website/
    ├── slips/
    ├── avatars/
    └── others/</pre>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
